      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ラタトスクモードが身体に与える影響が
心配だったから
一度話を聞かせてほしかったのよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I was concerned about the impact that
Ratatosk Mode might inflict on your body,
so I wanted to speak with you about it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だけど、何度手紙を送っても
エミルは来てくれなくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But no matter how many I sent you,
you never showed up...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ラタトスクモードは病気じゃないし
僕はぜんぜん大丈夫だったから。
心配かけて、ごめんなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ratatosk Mode isn't an illness or anything,
so everything's perfectly fine. I'm sorry
I made you worry like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだったんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that what it was...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア、ごめんなさい！
私、あなたの事、誤解してたみたい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria, I'm sorry! I guess I misunderstood you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいのよ、もう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル。
本当に身体の方は大丈夫なのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil. Is your body really doing okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どっちかって言うと
マルタに振り回されてる事の方が
身体への負担は大きいかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I had to pick one, Marta running me ragged
might be the bigger budern on my body...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごめんなさい、エミル！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sorry, Emil!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、ごめん、マルタ。
そんなつもりで言ったんじゃないんだ。
僕ならぜんぜん平気だから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, sorry, Marta. I didn't mean it like that.
I'm totally fine with it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
